graph LR
    TrainingOp[Training Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrainingOp -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    TrainingOp -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17.2]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano v1.8.0+]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| SchedulerPlugins[scheduler-plugins v0.26.7+]
    TrainingOp -.->|certificates| CertManager[cert-manager]
    TrainingOp -.->|metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    TrainingOp -.->|sidecar disabled| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio]

    %% Integration Points - Control Plane
    TrainingOp -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    K8sAPI -->|watches/creates| CRDs[Custom Resources<br/>PyTorchJob, TFJob, MPIJob, etc.]
    K8sAPI -->|manages| Pods[Training Pods]
    K8sAPI -->|manages| Services[Kubernetes Services]
    K8sAPI -->|manages| ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps]

    %% External Services
    TrainingOp -->|pull images| ContainerReg[Container Registry]
    Pods -->|datasets/checkpoints| S3[S3 Storage]
    Pods -->|shared data| NFS[NFS Storage]

    %% User Interaction
    DataScientist[Data Scientist] -->|kubectl apply| CRDs
    CISDK[CI/CD + Python SDK] -->|automate| CRDs

    %% Monitoring Integration
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI view<br/>not integrated| TrainingOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|can trigger| TrainingOp

    %% Styling
    style TrainingOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px

    %% External Required
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External Optional
    style Volcano fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style SchedulerPlugins fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CertManager fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PrometheusOp fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Kubernetes Resources
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CRDs fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Pods fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Services fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ConfigMaps fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333

    %% External Services
    style ContainerReg fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style NFS fill:#999,stroke:#333

    %% Users
    style DataScientist fill:#fff,stroke:#333
    style CISDK fill:#fff,stroke:#333

    %% ODH Components
    style Dashboard fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Pipelines fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
